{"tid":1099713,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"溫泉屋小女將  令新海誠落淚","createTime":"2019-04-10T03:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T09:13:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea50323ccc0669f89fe42741e146cb62e4b6b2f8","tid":1099713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.wmoov.com/movie/photo/201904/Okko27sInnPoster_1554113281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.wmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201904%2FOkko27sInnPoster_1554113281.jpg&h=260f9083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演 :<br />\n    高坂希太郎<br />\n演員 :<br />\n    --<br />\n片長 :<br />\n    --<br />\n級別 :<br />\n    --<br />\n語言 :<br />\n    日文 (中英文字幕)<br />\n上映 :<br />\n    18.4.2019 (公映) <br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n就讀小學六年級的小織在一場交通意外中不幸失去雙親，於是她便投靠經營著「春之屋」溫泉旅館的外婆峰子。在意外中倖存的小織，獲得了通靈力。在小織踏入春之屋旅館的第一天，她就看到旅館內有一個名叫誠仔的幽靈正默默地守護在外婆身邊！在旅館面臨後繼無人的困境下，小織決定在春之屋幫忙。因為小織的樂天性格及勇於接受挑戰，讓她逐變蛻變成一個能擔當重任的溫泉屋小女將。 不過，當小織漸漸成為人人喜愛的小女將後，她開始看不到這些幽靈朋友。此時，有一家同樣遇到交通意外的客人到訪，揭開了令小織意想不到的真相&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e82ea4a1d1bde7da7dfb2aef988e72790db0b4d4","tid":1099713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"《你的名字》的編劇兼導演新海誠表示：「《溫泉屋小女將》真是太精彩了！我被逗笑了好多次，也被惹哭了好幾次。作為動畫，不僅在技術上有許多可看之處，故事本身也相當動人，實在很期待可以繼續在大銀幕看到後續的故事啊！」日本媒體也讚賞該片：「寓教於樂，最具教育意義的親子成長電影。」<br />\n<br />\n熱銷300萬冊日本超人氣國民讀物改編、由曾參與製作《神隱少女》《怪物的孩子》等知名動畫作品的高坂希太郎執導、《電影版聲之形》編劇吉田玲子，人氣聲優水樹奈奈、松田颯水、以及童星出身的小林星蘭等人配音演出的勵志動畫電影《溫泉屋小女將》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/2/6/n11027102.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F2%2F6%2Fn11027102.htm&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=4553cd9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/2/6/n11027102.htm</a>"},{"pid":"23847ab1fcb7983575299b7cee060d7587845d30","tid":1099713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09rulkr3YWI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D09rulkr3YWI&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=b72d8b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09rulkr3YWI</a>"},{"pid":"5926525899669c6cd56369a855970b5e0b5e2dab","tid":1099713,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cf9fb68f6977fe6897cd2e8e21445c374954e1","tid":1099713,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/459v1nX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F459v1nX.png&h=8a4be633&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"796573f04d46903a93379dd2a6dae6f14277b5a3","tid":1099713,"uid":14591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"MCL復活節上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cd32f173631e3316bdef182d0d880b9c98eb66","tid":1099713,"uid":46389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"條友好似讚過好多片<br />\n唔知佢d審美觀係點"},{"pid":"84fa248507373ef011ee977415313e934922e023","tid":1099713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13cd32f173631e3316bdef182d0d880b9c98eb66","tid":1099713,"uid":46389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"條友好似讚過好多片<br />\n唔知佢d審美觀係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"邊幾部?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e47d4b7e5716881dfda12cdeb29f8dc7d5d9fe5","tid":1099713,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fa248507373ef011ee977415313e934922e023","tid":1